{"tid":2446745,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Google被發現 無痕模式繼續收集數據   面臨集體訴訟索償 50 億　","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T18:07:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3b0385f9f4363cb038f6d20c287c2b497f2398","tid":2446745,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"現在大部分瀏覽器都有類似「無痕模式」的功能，讓用家可以不留痕跡地上網，不過 Google Chrome 早前就被發現在開啓無痕模式之後，仍然會以各種方式追蹤用家，而 Google 就因此在美國面臨集體訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n提出集體訴訟的一方表示，Google 追蹤並收集用戶的瀏覽記錄以及其他網路活動，即使在開啓無痕模式之後仍然繼續，而且未有明確向用家解釋。Google 就解釋指他們已經清楚表示「無痕」模式並不是完全「隱身」，用家在使用期間的網絡活動仍然可能會被所瀏覽的網站以及第三方統計或廣告服務所收集。<br />\n<br />\n不過加州聖荷西地區法院就表示，Google 未有告知用家 Google 在無痕模式下仍然會收集數據，因此批准訴訟申請。今次集體訴訟是在去年六月提出，向 Google 索償 50 億美元，而 Google 雖然向法院方面申請訴訟無效但最近被駁回，之後案件將會交由加州北部區域法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/03/14/google-fails-to-block-5-billion-class-action-lawsuit/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F03%2F14%2Fgoogle-fails-to-block-5-billion-class-action-lawsuit%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfIOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=da674f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/03/14/google-fails-to-block-5-billion-class-action-lawsuit/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"e51438571802b8f5147a945de2e5659dee6baba9","tid":2446745,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8af06cb3d63b1929a440f5e45e10aa7c25992f7","tid":2446745,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTi